					<p class="text-white prose-xl font-black">Say yes</p>
					<p class="text-white">Embrace time efficiency — collaborate with a technical specialist in days, not months.</p>
					<p class="text-white">Ensure quality and control risk — our expertise safeguards your investment.</p>
